{"tid":697143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（文明古國）中國山寨獅身人面像又重組 埃及痛批：極其無禮","createTime":"2018-06-10T17:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T06:26:56.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"447c92a31aa46ac9d87875c0f47ca3a128575a07","tid":697143,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:04:54.000Z","msg":"中國河北石家莊的山寨人面獅身像，2年前因埃及向聯合國教科文組織投訴而拆除，近日卻又傳出山寨人面獅身像準備重新組裝，引發埃及國內的憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，中國河北省的石家莊市，在2014年以1：1的比例仿造埃及「獅身人面像」，引發埃及強烈的不滿；埃及古物部部長認為，山寨版人面獅身像細節處理粗糙，與原版差距大，會影響到遊客對埃及古文物原貌的瞭解失真，褻瀆埃及文化遺產，同時中國的山寨行為，明顯觸犯聯合國於1974年締下的世界文化和自然遺產保護公約，要求中國索賠，或自行將仿製品拆除。<br />\n該園區辯稱是拍戲用的臨時性場景，拍攝完了就拆除改景，2016年將「人面」拆卸下來，此後該人面獅身像就一直維持身首分離的形態，但傳出近日園方又再度將山寨人面獅身像重組，有施工人員指出，此次工程不僅是將「人面」和「獅身」接在一起，還將進行一些改造工作，至於改造細節，工人並不清楚。<br />\n據《俄羅斯衛星網》報導，山寨人面獅身像重新組建，再度引發了埃及國內憤怒的浪潮，埃及文物部表示，準備重新向聯合國教科文組織和中國外交部提出拆除山寨品，痛批此舉是對埃及文明遺產極其無禮的態度。<br />\n不過，除了河北石家莊，中國山寨人面獅身像也出現在甘肅蘭州、安徽滁州等地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2453465\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2453465&d=7dik%2B57InS7eQz7adFhe%2FZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=32830143\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2453465&h=36908c67\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2453465</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6b60f37ec5428977953304899b8fb36dc5f6eb","tid":697143,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb2bb525f442b9ded5cc7d2864d1c6acc690dc1","tid":697143,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:57:27.000Z","msg":"咁叻不如整個1:1嘅金字塔出黎"},{"pid":"78daf7f28d809ad561f64b3f30d8b42916d13306","tid":697143,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/48338382g76d89b51e5e1&amp;690\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F48338382g76d89b51e5e1%26690&h=0b569a23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1115f786d2b21b86c6bcf3d32a4ed00b32f45d1d","tid":697143,"uid":1863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:26:22.000Z","msg":"獅身人面像(唐氏綜合症)"},{"pid":"9a8ab974e5df828844a5bb9828322d9962f4aa39","tid":697143,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:26:53.000Z","msg":"不過，除了河北石家莊，中國山寨人面獅身像也出現在甘肅蘭州、安徽滁州等地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56d2e3992be56c8c47182c5195d478b52cbeabc","tid":697143,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:26:56.000Z","msg":"佢應該係想換習帝個頭上去啫~"}]}